    public class ScanResultsFragment
extends androidx.fragment.app.DialogFragment
    This class creates a Dialog Fragment to show the name and score of a QR Code the user has just scanned. It also processes QR Code data to be viewed in detail if the user wishes to do so References: 1. https://www.javatpoint.com/java-get-current-date 2. https://firebase.google.com/docs/firestore/manage-data/add-data
